overview: They’re young, snazzy and have got four wheels beneath their feet – but believe us when we tell you that it’s not fast cars that interest these horned-up buddies. No, the likes of Charlie Keller, Titus Snow and Connor Rex are all self-confessed skater-boys; whose love of boarding is only matched by their love of hard cock and hot spunk! Fortunately for us, it’s that latter interest that sparks our focus here, as the lads team up for a jizz-soaked round of ass-stretching, ball-draining fun that’ll leave you gasping for a bout at your local skater-park!
title: Raw Skaters
